{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Intended to be assigned to the Down arrow in the MIDI Editor, this action simulates pressing Down in musical notation software such as Dorico by guessing how many bars the music is zoomed by. If in a different MIDI editor mode, decreases the pitch cursor, which goes "down" in that view.\par}
}

